20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20last%20rites%20will%20be%20held%20with%20full%20state%20honours%20in%20Mandya%20district%20tomorrow.%20The%20Karnataka%20government%20has%20also%20announced%20a%20three-day%20state%20mourning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20figure%20in%20making%20Bengaluru%20a%20tech%20capital%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsm-krishna-dies-somanahalli-mallaiah-krishna-dies-who-was-sm-krishna-veteran-politician-who-put-bengaluru-on-global-map-7212552%5C%22%3ESM%C2%A0Krishna%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20born%20in%20Somanahalli%20in%20Mandya%20district%20on%20May%201%2C%201932.%20Having%20served%20a%20long%20stint%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20his%20political%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20he%20was%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20Mr%20Krishna's%20death.%20Calling%20him%20a%C2%A0remarkable%20leader%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20always%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20improve%20the%20lives%20of%20others.%20He%20is%20fondly%20remembered%20for%20his%20tenure%20as%20Karnataka's%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20particularly%20for%20his%20focus%20on%20infrastructural%20development.%20Shri%20SM%20Krishna%20Ji%20was%20also%20a%20prolific%20reader%20and%20thinker.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocked%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20news.%20He%20said%20that%20Mr%20Krishna's%20service%20as%20a%20State%20and%20Union%20Minister%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20is%20unparalleled.%20%26quot%3BKarnataka%20will%20always%20be%20indebted%20to%20him%20for%20his%20contribution%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20IT-BT%20sector%2C%20especially%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20politician%20guided%20him%20during%20his%20early%20days%20of%20joining%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20said%20he%20was%20a%20true%20leader%20who%20always%20prioritised%20the%20welfare%20of%20his%20people.%20%26quot%3BOur%20friendship%20transcended%20the%20competitive%20spirit%20we%20shared%20in%20attracting%20investments%20to%20our%20respective%20states.%20He%20was%20a%20true%20leader%20who%20always%20prioritized%20the%20welfare%20of%20his%20people.%20My%20heartfelt%20condolences%20go%20out%20to%20his%20family%20and%20friends%20during%20this%20difficult%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Krishna%20graduated%20from%20the%20Maharaja's%20College%20in%20Mysuru%20and%20obtained%20a%20law%20degree%20from%20the%20Government%20Law%20College%20in%20Bengaluru.%20He%20later%20went%20to%20the%20US%20to%20study%20at%20the%20Southern%20Methodist%20University%20in%20Dallas%20and%20the%20George%20Washington%20University%20as%20a%20Fulbright%20Scholar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20political%20career%20began%20in%201962%20when%20he%20won%20the%20Maddur%20assembly%20seat%20as%20an%20Independent%20-%20defeating%20prominent%20Congress%20politician%20KV%20Shankar%20Gowda%20-%20and%20became%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly.%20He%20made%20his%20parliament%20debut%20in%201968%20after%20winning%20the%20Mandya%20by-election%2C%20but%20resigned%20and%20returned%20to%20state%20politics%20in%201972.%20He%20went%20back%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%201980.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20became%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%201971%20after%20being%20with%20the%20Praja%20Socialist%20Party%20for%20some%20time.%20In%201999%2C%20he%20led%20the%20Congress%20to%20victory%20as%20the%20state%20unit%20chief%20and%20became%20the%20chief%20minister.%20He%20served%20as%20the%20Governor%20of%20Maharashtra%20from%202004%20to%202008%20and%20became%20the%20foreign%20minister%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733810100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fnkoldfl8_sm-krishna_625x300_10_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Find