%20Message%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EReserve%20Bank%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20the%20fiscal-monetary%20coordination%20was%20at%20its%20best%20during%20the%20last%20six%20years%20even%20as%20he%20thanked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20giving%20the%20opportunity%20to%20head%20the%20monetary%20authority%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Das%2C%20in%20a%20series%20of%20posts%20on%20X%2C%20on%20his%20last%20day%20of%20his%20six-year%20term%20as%20RBI%20Governor%2C%20also%20thanked%20the%20Finance%20Minister%2C%20various%20stakeholders%20and%20his%20colleagues%20at%20the%20central%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImmensely%20grateful%20to%20the%20Hon'ble%20PM%20%40narendramodi%20for%20giving%20me%20this%20opportunity%20to%20serve%20the%20country%20as%20Governor%20RBI%20and%20for%20his%20guidance%20and%20encouragement.%20Benefited%20a%20lot%20from%20his%20ideas%20and%20thoughts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20from%20his%20personal%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20gratitude%20to%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20for%20her%20constant%20support%20and%20backing%2C%20he%20said%2C%20fiscal-monetary%20coordination%20was%20at%20its%20best%20and%20helped%20to%20deal%20with%20multiple%20challenges%20during%20the%20last%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20thanked%20all%20the%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20financial%20sector%20and%20in%20the%20economy%3B%20experts%20and%20economists%3B%20industry%20bodies%20and%20associations%3B%20organisations%20in%20the%20agriculture%2C%20cooperative%20and%20service%20sectors%20for%20their%20inputs%20and%20policy%20suggestions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20BIG%20thank%20you%20to%20the%20entire%20Team%20RBI.%20Together%2C%20we%20successfully%20navigated%20an%20exceptionally%20difficult%20period%20of%20unprecedented%20global%20shocks.%20May%20the%20RBI%20grow%20even%20taller%20as%20an%20institution%20of%20trust%20and%20credibility.%20My%20best%20wishes%20to%20each%20one%20of%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20another%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Das%20was%20appointed%20the%2025th%20RBI%20Governor%20in%20December%202018%2C%20after%20the%20sudden%20resignation%20of%20Urjit%20Patel%20amid%20a%20tussle%20between%20RBI%20and%20the%20government%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20surplus%20transfer%20and%20autonomy%20of%20the%20regulator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20taking%20over%2C%20he%20not%20only%20settled%20the%20storm%20amicably%20related%20to%20surplus%20transfer%20but%20assuaged%20the%20concerns%20of%20the%20markets.%20Not%20once%20since%20he%20took%20over%20did%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20RBI%20autonomy%20hit%20the%20headlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20stint%2C%20RBI%20provided%20record%20dividends%20to%20the%20government.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20handed%20over%20the%20highest-ever%20dividend%20of%20Rs%202.11%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20governance%20has%20always%20been%20in%20sync%20with%20what%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20wanted%20in%20an%20RBI%20chief%2C%20after%20the%20successive%20stints%20of%20Raghuram%20Rajan%20and%20Urjit%20Patel%2C%20which%20were%20marred%20by%20constant%20conflicts%20between%20the%20RBI%20and%20the%20Finance%20Ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20deftly%20steered%20India's%20monetary%20policy%20response%20during%20the%20challenging%20period%20of%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20previous%20avatar%2C%20Das%20as%20Economic%20Affairs%20Secretary%20and%20Revenue%20Secretary%20was%20the%20key%20man%20behind%20the%20planning%20and%20execution%20of%20the%20demonetisation%20drive%20and%20rollout%20of%20the%20landmark%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Das%2C%20a%201980%20batch%20IAS%20officer%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20cadre%2C%20retired%20as%20Secretary%20of%20Department%20of%20Economic%20Affairs%20in%20May%202018.%20Post-retirement%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%