ictions.%20Born%20Michel%20de%20Nostredame%2C%20Nostradamus%20was%20a%20French%20astrologer%20and%20physician%20who%20lived%20in%20the%201500s%20and%20predicted%20some%20of%20the%20modern-day%20epochal%20moments%20such%20as%20Adolf%20Hitler's%20rise%20to%20power%2C%20the%20September%2011%20attacks%20and%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20He%20is%20best%20known%20for%20his%20book%20Les%20Prophetis%20(The%20Prophecies)%2C%20published%20in%201555%2C%20which%20contains%20942%20poetic%20quatrains%20that%20are%20widely%20interpreted%20for%20global%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearchers%20analysing%20his%20work%20have%20hinted%20that%202025%20may%20have%20some%20hard-hitting%20events%20in%20store%2C%20ranging%20from%20an%20asteroid%20collision%20to%20another%20plague-like%20outbreak%20in%20the%20UK.%20Though%20Nostradamus'%20prophecies%20more%20often%20than%20not%20miss%20the%20mark%2C%20they%20do%20provide%20a%20certain%20thrill%20to%20the%20people%20reading%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnd%20of%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENostradamus'%202024%20prediction%20included%20the%20continuation%20of%20a%20continent-wide%20war%20but%20as%20per%20his%20vague%20writings%2C%202025%20may%20witness%20a%20potential%20end%20to%20one%20of%20the%20long-running%20wars.%20The%20astrologer%20said%20owing%20to%20the%20exhaustion%20of%20the%20war%2C%20perhaps%20referring%20to%20the%20ongoing%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20that%20started%20in%202022%2C%20both%20sides%20may%20call%20it%20quits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20long%20war%20all%20the%20army%20exhausted%2Cso%20that%20they%20do%20not%20find%20money%20for%20the%20soldiers%3B%20instead%20of%20gold%20or%20silver%2C%20they%20will%20come%20to%20coin%20leather%2C%20Gallic%20brass%2C%20and%20the%20crescent%20sign%20of%20the%20Moon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mention%20of%20%26quot%3BGallic%20brass%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsign%20of%20the%20moon%26quot%3B%20has%20led%20social%20media%20users%20to%20believe%20that%20France%20and%20Turkey%20may%20get%20involved%20in%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlague%20and%20war%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENostradamus%20has%20predicted%20that%20the%20new%20year%20will%20weigh%20heavily%20on%20England%20which%20will%20be%20beset%20by%20%26quot%3Bcruel%20wars'%20and%20face%20an%20%26quot%3Bancient%20plague%26quot%3B%20outbreak%20that%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bworse%20than%20enemies%26quot%3B.%20Since%20his%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20prediction%20came%20true%2C%20experts%20have%20put%20a%20pin%20on%20this%20prophecy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2C%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fliving-nostradamus-claims-four-prophecies-fulfilled-predicts-more-unforeseen-events-6564988%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20'Living%20Nostradamus'%20Claims%20Four%20Prophecies%20Fulfilled%2C%20Predicts%20More%20Unforeseen%20Events%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAsteroid%20collision%20with%20Earth%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20other%20events%20may%20not%20cause%20civilisation%20loss%2C%20Nostradamus%20has%20predicted%20that%202025%20may%20witness%20a%20giant%20asteroid%20collodion%20with%20the%20Earth%2C%20or%20coming%20in%20dangerous%20proximity%20to%20the%20planet.%20Though%20the%20prediction%20might%20suggest%20a%20wipeout%20of%20life%20from%20Earth%2C%20asteroids%20coming%20close%20to%20the%20planet%20is%20not%20a%20new%20phenomenon.%20Several%20hundred%20asteroids%20whiz%20past%20Earth%20every%20year%20with%20the%20majority%20of%20them%20maintaining%20a%20safe%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENatural%20disasters%20in%20Brazil%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prophecy%20also%20stated%20that%20the%20South%20American%20country%20of%20Brazil%2C%20which%20Nostradamus%20refers%20to%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BGarden%20of%20the%20World%26quot%3B%2C%20may%20face%20flooding%20and%20potential%20volcanic%20activity%2C%20linked%20to%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGarden%20of%20the%20world%20near%20the%20new%20city%2C%20In%20the%20path%20of%20the%20hollow%20mountains%3A%20It%20will%20be%20seized%20and%20plunged%20into%20the%20Tub%2C%20Forced%20to%20drink%20waters%20poisoned%20by%20sulfur%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20eerie%20piece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Nostradamus'%20bleak%20worldview%20stems%20from%20heavy%20consumption%20of%20the%20Old%20Testament%20and%20the%20trauma%20of%20losing%20his%20wife%20and%20young%20children%20to%20illness%2C%20presumably%20the%20plague.%20Unable%20to%20save%20his%20loved%20one%2C%20Nostradamus%20sought%20solace%20in%20predicting%20doom%20and%20gloom%20that%20may%20befall%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733801700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F28l5ahjo_nostradamus_625x300_31_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fnostradamus-predictions-for-2025-asteroid-collision-to-plague-like-outbreak-and-more-7212856%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Though%20Nostradamus'%20prophecies%20more%20often%20than%20not%20miss%20the%20mark%2C%20they%20do%20provide%20a%20certain%20thrill%20to%20the%20people%20reading%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fnostradamus-predictions-for-2025-asteroid-collision-to-plague-like-outbreak-and-more-7212856%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22FIR%20filed%20against%20'BMCM'%20director%20Ali%20Abbas%20Zafar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733801435000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116155318%2Cimgsize-101072.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fbade-miyan-chote-miyan-row-fir-filed-against-ali-abbas-zafar-as-vashu-bha