e%20joined%20the%20underworld%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733800607000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116155354%2Cimgsize-25166.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnana-patekar-if-i-had-not-become-an-actor-i-would-have-been-in-the-underworld%2Farticleshow%2F116155377.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116155377.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVeteran%20actor%20Nana%20Patekar%20recently%20spoke%20about%20his%20fiery%20past%2C%20including%20his%20infamous%20clash%20with%20director%20Sanjay%20Leela%20Bhansali.%20In%20an%20interview%2C%20Patekar%20admitted%20to%20his%20volatile%20nature%2C%20suggesting%20he%20might%20have%20been%20drawn%20to%20the%20underworld%20if%20not%20for%20acting.%20He%20confessed%20to%20past%20physical%20altercations%20and%20acknowledged%20that%20his%20temper%20intimidated%20others.%20Patekar%20detailed%20his%20disagreements%20with%20Bhansali%20during%20the%20filming%20of%20%26quot%3BKhamoshi%2C%26quot%3B%20admitting%20his%20harsh%20words%20likely%20caused%20offense.%20While%20expressing%20regret%20and%20missing%20their%20collaboration%2C%20he%20also%20hinted%20at%20a%20possible%20reconciliation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnana-patekar-if-i-had-not-become-an-actor-i-would-have-been-in-the-underworld%2Farticleshow%2F116155377.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BParasites...%26quot%3B%3A%20Document%20Found%20With%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Murder%20Suspect%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELuigi%20Mangione%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20Ivy%20League%20graduate%20who%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20person%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Manhattan%20killing%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%2C%20was%20reportedly%20carrying%20a%20manifesto%20railing%20against%20%26quot%3Bcorporate%20America%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20arrest.%20The%20two-page%20handwritten%20document%20criticized%20the%20healthcare%20industry%20for%20putting%20profits%20above%20care%20and%20suggested%20that%20violence%20is%20the%20answer%2C%20according%20to%20senior%20law%20enforcement%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20apologize%20for%20any%20strife%20and%20trauma%2C%20but%20it%20had%20to%20be%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20police%20official%20who%20has%20seen%20the%20document%20told%20CNN.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20note%2C%20Mangione%20said%20he%20acted%20alone%20and%20that%20he%20was%20self-funded.%20%26quot%3BThese%20parasites%20had%20it%20coming%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20also%20included%20a%20screed%20against%20the%20healthcare%20industry%2C%20with%20Mangione%20lamenting%20the%20costs%20of%20healthcare%2C%20asking%20why%20the%20United%20States%20has%20the%20most%20expensive%20healthcare%20in%20the%20world%20but%20is%20rated%20poorly%20for%20life%20expectancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20reportedly%20ranked%2049%20in%20life%20expectancy%20in%202022%2C%20per%20a%20report%20by%20the%20Associated%20Press%20story%20from%20August%202007.%20However%2C%20the%20country%20is%20expected%20to%20drop%20to%2066th%20position%20globally%20in%202050%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Institute%20for%20Health%20Metrics%20and%20Evaluation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20motive%20of%20Thompson's%20killing%20is%20still%20unknown%2C%20reports%20suggest%20Mangione's%20alleged%20actions%20could%20have%20been%20a%20political%20act.%20If%20%C2%A0Mangione%20is%20found%20guilty%20of%20Thompson's%20murder%2C%20the%20manifesto%20would%20be%20the%20second%20message%20from%20him.%20Earlier%2C%20it%20was%20found%20that%20the%20killer%20engraved%20'Deny%2C%20defend%2C%20depose'%20on%20the%20casings%20of%20the%20bullet%20used%20in%20the%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO's%20killing.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELuigi%20Mangione's%20Arrest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20manifesto%2C%20Mangione%20was%20also%20found%20carrying%20a%20gun%2C%20and%20a%20silencer%2C%20among%20other%20items%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20arrest%20in%20an%20Altoona%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20McDonald's.%20He%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20possession%20of%20an%20illegal%20weapon%2C%20forgery%20and%20other%20crimes%20in%20Pennsylvania%20after%20being%20arrested%20at%20a%20McDonald's%20on%20Monday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20was%20caught%20after%20an%20employee%20at%20the%20fast-food%20chain%20recognized%20him%20and%20alerted%20the%20police.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20sitting%20there%20eating%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Guardian%20reported%20Joseph%20Kenny%2C%20the%20New%20York%20City%20police%20department's%20chief%20of%20detectives%20as%20saying.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20reportedly%20found%20carrying%20identification%20with%20his%20name%20on%20it%2C%20along%20with%20a%20fake%20New%20Jersey%20ID%20-%20the%20same%20that%20police%20believe%20the%20gunman%20showed%20when%20he%20checked%20into%20a%20hostel%20on%20the%20Upper%20West%20Side%20of%20Manhattan%20on%2024%20November%20after%20Thompson's%20murder.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO's%20killing%20in%20broad%20daylight%20shocked%20many%20Americans%20but%20also%20sparked%20an%20outrage%20at%20the%20US's%20profit-driven%20healthcare%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20Luigi%20Mangione%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMangione%20social%20media%20presence%20shows%20that%20he%20belongs%20to%20a%20well-to-do%20family.%20Per%20his%20LinkedIn%20page%2C%20he%20has%20a%20bachelor's%20and%20master's%20degree%20in%20science%20engineering%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania.%20The%20claims%20were%20confirmed%20by%20a%20university%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20suspect%20was%20reportedly%20born%20and%20raised%20in%20Maryland%20and%20has%20lived%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20Honolulu.%20As%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2024%2Fdec%2F09%2Funitedhealthcare-ceo-shooting-suspect-arrested%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereport%2C%20he%20was%20a%20valedictorian%20at%20Gilman%20High%20School%20in%202016%2C%20where%20he%20had%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20study%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20Ni%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2Fus%2Flive-news%2Fbrian-thompson-unitedhealthcare-death-investigation-12-9-24%23cm4hdmno4000b3b6mea2l9cef%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20Mangione%20is%20the%20grandson%20of%20Nicholas%20Mangione%2C%20a%20prominent%20Baltimore%20real%20estate%20developer.%20The%20Mangione%20family%20reportedly%20owns%20Lorien%20Health%20Systems%2C%20a%20nursing%20home%20chain%20in%20Maryland%2C%20where%20the%20suspect%20volunteered%20in%202014%2C%20according%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733799960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fecntjad8_unitedhealthcare-ceo-brian-thompson-killer-luigi-mangione-twitter_625x300_10_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fparasites-document-found-with-unitedhealthcare-ceo-murder-suspect-7212733%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Luigi%20Mangione%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20Ivy%20League%20graduate%20who%20is%20%26quot%3Bperson%20of%20interest%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Manhattan%20killing%20of%20UnitedHealthcare%20CEO%20Brian%20Thompson%2C%20was%20reportedly%20carrying%20a%20manifesto%20railing%20against%20%26quot%3Bcorpora