s%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Binstitution%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20two%20years%20investing%20and%20investing%20and%20not%20seeing%20anything%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20Lerner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20October%20report%20from%20Evident%20AI%2C%20which%20tracks%20AI%20adoption%20in%20financial%20services%2C%20only%20six%20out%20of%2050%20banks%20disclosed%20dollar-level%20cost%20savings%20or%20revenue%20lifts%20as%20a%20result%20of%20their%20AI%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20separates%20the%20frontrunners%20from%20the%20laggards%3F%20According%20to%20fresh%20research%20from%20McKinsey%2C%20it%20can%20come%20down%20to%20a%20few%20key%20decisions%20around%20concentrating%20efforts%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20uses%2C%20having%20CEO%20buy-in%2C%20and%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-banks-using-agents-generative-ai-fintechs-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20conjunction%20with%20other%20technologies.%20Most%20of%20all%2C%20it'll%20involve%20a%20mindset%20shift%20where%20AI%20is%20viewed%20and%20treated%20as%20a%20business%20opportunity%20rather%20than%20a%20technological%20problem%2C%20Lerner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELerner%20outlined%20what%20will%20separate%20the%20winners%20from%20the%20losers.%20He%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20specific%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e473fadf-dc3a-47ba-89e5-c622f9ca79c4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EViewing%20AI%20as%20a%20business%20problem%2C%20not%20a%20tech%20one%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELeadership%20teams%20have%20to%20recognize%20that%20generative%20AI%20is%20a%20business%20opportunity%2C%20not%20just%20a%20technology%20play%2C%20Lerner%20said.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20he%20said%20business%20leaders%20should%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20accountability%2C%20rather%20than%20that%20responsibility%20falling%20solely%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcto-cio-top-jobs-wall-street-goldman-sachs-citadel-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20leaders'%20shoulders.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20institutions%20that%20make%20business%20leaders%20accountable%20for%20delivering%20their%20results%20will%20over%20time%20tend%20to%20do%20better%20because%20there's%20a%20much%20stronger%20partnership%2C%26quot%3B%20Lerner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef97ddc1-80da-4571-ba77-51b515d9af90%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EConcentrating%20firepower%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20has%20lead%20to%20more%20value%20when%20there%20are%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20use%20cases%2C%20instead%20of%20every%20business%20unit%20doing%20a%20little%20bit%20here%20and%20there%20and%20seeing%20what%20sticks%2C%20Lerner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%20of%20having%2060%20use%20cases%20across%2015%20different%20business%20lines%20and%20functions%2C%20narrow%20down%20to%20three%20areas%20where%20you%20want%20to%20go%20deep%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20you're%20reimagining%20the%20entire%20domain%20or%20workflow%20has%20led%20to%20a%20faster%20path%20to%20value%2C%20Lerner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22735c176d-aebc-480d-8418-a288aa528e55%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EChoose%20areas%20where%20ROI%20can%20actually%20be%20tracked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20becoming%20increasingly%20clear%20that%20generative%20AI's%20main%20strength%20in%20saving%20workers%20time%20can't%20always%20be%20traced%20back%20to%20bottom-line%20impact%2C%20which%20is%20leading%20to%20some%20frustration%20in%20the%20boardroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20value%20of%20what%20you're%20doing%20depends%20on%20how%20you're%20going%20to%20repurpose%20your%20time%2C%20and%20that's%20really%20hard%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Lerner%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20it's%20an%20indirect%20sort%20of%20lever%2C%20it's%20very%20difficult%20to%20actually%20measure%20and%20get%20people%20to%20agree%20that%20there's%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20AI%20tools%20like%20call-center%20copilots%20and%20AI-powered%20marketing%20campaigns%20that%20improve%20the%20customer%20experience%20can%20generate%20incremental%20value%20that%20is%20measurable%2C%20Lerner%20said.%20One%20large%20bank%20referenced%20in%20the%20McKinsey%20report%20is%20projecting%20a%2010%25%20revenue%20increase%20thanks%20to%20a%20new%20analytics%20platform%20to%20target%20new%20customers%20and%20cross-sell%20products%20to%20existing%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20buy%20now%2C%20pay%20later%20fintech%20Klarna%2C%20leveraging%20an%20OpenAI-powered%20call%20center%20agent%20is%20estimated%20to%20bring%20some%20%2440%20million%20in%20profit%20this%20year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.klarna.com%2Finternational%2Fpress%2Fklarna-ai-assistant-handles-two-thirds-of-customer-service-chats-in-its-first-month%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20earlier%20this%20year.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20AI%20was%20doing%20the%20work%20of%20700%20full-time%20agents%2C%20according%20to%20Klarna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELerner%20said%20he's%20starting%20to%20see%20some%20banks%20modify%20forward-looking%20hiring%20plans%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20contact%20center%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20increase%20in%20self-service%20and%20faster%20resolution%20times.%20%26quot%3BThat%20cost%20avoidance%20is%20absolutely%20measurable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef12ec85-427f-4bfe-af1d-73db55a6f586%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EReusability%20is%20key%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBuild%20something%20once%20and%20redeploy%20it%20a%20hundred%20times%2C%20Lerner%20said.%20Doing%20so%20can%20accelerate%20development%20times%20and%20let%20companies%20scale%20faster%20because%20the%20tool%20has%20already%20gone%20through%20the%20required%20risk%2C%20security%2C%20and%20compliance%20approvals%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22010675d6-b59b-4647-bb42-a06216752d0e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EExecution%20will%20come%20down%20to%20adoption%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20workers%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-marco-argenti-wall-street-ai-tech-qa-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomers%20to%20adopt%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20new%20way%20of%20doing%20something%20or%20a%20new%20technology%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20parts%20of%20the%20value%20equation.%20It's%20an%20old%20challenge%20that%20banks%20have%20had%20with%20previous%20technology%20cycles.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20AI%2C%20%26quot%3Bmost%20companies%20have%20done%20a%20pretty%20bad%20job%20of%20getting%20adoption%20to%20the%20level%20that's%20going%20to%20yield%20the%20results%20that%20they%20want%20to%20yield%2C%26quot%3B%20Lerner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wall-street-banks-can-find-roi-ai-investments-mckinsey-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733785321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6113e976b1e9390018755718%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wall-street-banks-can-find-roi-ai-investments-mckinsey-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bank%20leaders%20want%20to%20see%20results%20from%20AI%20investments%2C%20but%20many%20banks%20are%20stuck%20in%20a%20proof-of-concept%20%26quot%3Bpurgatory%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20McKinsey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Bianca%20Chan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wall-street-banks-can-find-roi-ai-investments-mckinsey-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Endless%20Summer%20Syndrome%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20A%20Shocking%20Allegation%20Disturbs%20a%20Family%20Holiday%20in%20a%20Disquieting%20French%2