een%20an%20issue%2C%20but%20I%20realised%20we%20had%20to%20find%20a%20sustainable%20solution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20vision%20for%20water%20conservation%20began%20with%20creating%20a%20structure%20that%20would%20not%20only%20store%20water%20but%20also%20reduce%20dependence%20on%20external%20sources.%20In%202015-16%2C%20he%20spearheaded%20the%20creation%20of%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20people-made%20dams%20on%20the%20Manganga%20River%20in%20Dahiwadi.%20The%20project%20marked%20a%20significant%20milestone%20for%20the%20community%2C%20which%20came%20together%2C%20inspired%20by%20Abhay%E2%80%99s%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20this%20project%20was%20transformative.%20The%20tanker%20trucks%2C%20which%20had%20once%20been%20a%20regular%20sight%20in%20Dahiwadi%2C%20no%20longer%20needed%20to%20deliver%20water.%20The%20community%20now%20had%20access%20to%20a%20reliable%20water%20source.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20saved%20crores%20of%20rupees%20by%20eliminating%20the%20cost%20of%20buying%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abhay%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dam%20gave%20us%20the%20ability%20to%20survive%20even%20if%20there%20were%20years%20without%20rainfall.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhay%E2%80%99s%20success%20in%20Dahiwadi%20became%20the%20spark%20that%20fuelled%20a%20larger%20movement.%20Motivated%20by%20the%20positive%20impact%20his%20village%20had%20experienced%2C%20Abhay%20expanded%20his%20efforts%20to%20other%20villages%20in%20the%20region.%20From%202018%20to%202024%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20from%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fem%3EArt%20of%20Living%E2%80%99%20reached%2064%20villages%2C%20focusing%20on%20water%20conservation%20initiatives%2C%20organic%20farming%2C%20and%20youth%20leadership%20development.%20Collaborating%20with%20organisations%20like%20the%20%E2%80%98Paani%20Foundation%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20by%20Bollywood%20actor%20Aamir%20Khan