onservation%20efforts.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20first%2C%20only%208-10%20people%20were%20interested%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abhay%20recalls.%20But%20instead%20of%20giving%20up%2C%20Abhay%20invited%2025%20children%20with%20disabilities%20to%20participate%20in%20rallies%2C%20focusing%20on%20Shramdaan%20(labour%20donation).%20These%20rallies%20soon%20captured%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20entire%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20villagers%2C%20Sujata%20Waghmare%2C%20admits%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Abhay%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20first%20introduced%20the%20water%20conservation%20project%20in%20our%20village%2C%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20really%20interested.%20But%20when%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20attend%20the%20training%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20The%20training%20was%20so%20impactful%20that%20I%20immediately%20realised%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%20cause.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbhay%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20brought%20so%20much%20energy%20and%20enthusiasm%20to%20the%20project%20that%20it%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20his%20village.%20His%20passion%20motivated%20me%20to%20get%20actively%20involved%2C%20attending%20meetings%20and%20joining%20the%20projects.%20I%20also%20encouraged%20others%20to%20take%20part%20so%20they%20could%20understand%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332290%2Fmaharashtra-water-scarcity-drought-prone-jalna-district-gets-aid-water-bodies-desilted%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20water%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20amazed%20me%20most%20was%20that%20even%20though%20Abhay%20sir%20is%20physically%20disabled%2C%20his%20drive%20to%20work%20is%20beyond%20inspiring%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20villagers%20became%20engaged%2C%20Pingali-Kd%20raised%20the%20necessary%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F247233%2Fbori-bandh-check-dam-ajay-s