0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducational%20achievements%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20easily%20accessible%2C%20even%20after%20completing%20their%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDo%20I%20need%20to%20register%20for%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20and%20how%20do%20I%20get%20started%20with%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20you%20have%20to%20register%20for%20the%20APAAR%20ID.%20To%20register%2C%20visit%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC%20Bank)%20website%20%E2%80%93%20abc.gov.in%20and%20click%20on%20%E2%80%98My%20Account%2C%E2%80%99%20then%20select%20the%20%E2%80%98Student%E2%80%99%20option.%20Next%2C%20click%20%E2%80%98Sign%20up%E2%80%99%20and%20provide%20your%20mobile%20number%2C%20address%2C%20and%20Aadhaar%20card%20details%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F217362%2Fhow-to-get-cbse-10-12-examination-marksheet-migration-certification-online-digilocker-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20a%20DigiLocker%20account%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20logging%20in%20with%20your%20credentials%2C%20DigiLocker%20will%20prompt%20you%20to%20consent%20to%20share%20your%20Aadhaar%20card%20details%20with%20ABC%20for%20KYC%20verification.%20Once%20you%20agree%2C%20enter%20your%20academic%20details%2C%20such%20as%20your%20school%20or%20university%20name%2C%20class%2C%20and%20course.%20After%20submitting%20the%20form%2C%20your%20APAAR%20ID%20card%20will%20be%20generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20you%20download%20your%20APAAR%20ID%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20APAAR%20ID%20can%20be%20easily%20downloaded%20by%20logging%20into%20the%20Academic%20Bank%20of%20Credits%20(ABC%20Bank)%20website.%20Once%20logged%20in%2C%20students%20can%20navigate%20to%20the%20dashboard%20and%20select%20the%20%E2%80%98APAAR%20card%20download%E2%80%99%20option.%20The%20card%20will%20then%20appear%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20ready%20to%20be%20downloaded%20or%20printed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDisclaimer%3A%20We%20will%20update%20the%20latest%20information%20about%20the%20APAAR%20ID%20card%20when%20more%20details%20are%20revealed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733318268000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-mobile-1732080263.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D386210%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20APAAR%20ID%2C%20launched%20in%202023%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India%2C%20provides%20a%20digital%20identity%20that%20helps%20students%20manage%20and%20access%20their%20academic%20records%20across%20multiple%20institutions.%20This%2012-digit%20ID%20consolidates%20information%20like%20marksheets%2C%20degrees%2C%20and%20co-curricular%20achievements%20into%20a%20single%20platform%2C%20simplifying%20academic%20transitions%20and%20tracking%20progress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Raajwrita%20Dutta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386210%2Fhow-apaar-id-works-answers-to-all-your-questions-about-this-student-id-system%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Legal%20Expert%20Shares%20Tips%20for%20Resolving%20Disputes%20Outside%20the%20Courtroom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EResolving%20disputes%20through%20traditional%20courts%20can%20be%20a